This article is a Presidential Memorandum issued by President Donald J. Trump on April 4, 2018. The memorandum delegates authorities under Section 3136 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2018 to the Secretary of Energy. This delegation is done in coordination with the Secretary of State, Secretary of Defense, Secretary of Homeland Security, and the Director of National Intelligence. The memorandum states that these delegations will also apply to any future public laws that have provisions similar to the one mentioned in the memorandum. The Secretary of Energy is directed to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.